                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td>2</td>
                      <td>
                        Model Name <small class="text-muted">(Required)</small>
                      </td>
                      <td>
                        - Enter model name which is already entered in Model
                        table
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td>3</td>
                      <td>
                        Car Images <small class="text-muted">(Required)</small>
                      </td>
                      <td>
                        - Enter paths of all your images in this filed<br />-
                        Make sure that use coma(,) seperation between 2 paths
                        <br />
                        - Don't use space between 2 paths<br />- Enter
