                        For example,
                        <br />https://cloud.aviansoft.in/car%20images/NON%20EV/Audi%20Q5/Audi%20Q5%20Exterior%204.jpg,
                        https://cloud.aviansoft.in/car%20images/NON%20EV/Audi%20Q5/Audi%20Q5%20Exterior%206.jpg,
                        https://cloud.aviansoft.in/car%20images/NON%20EV/Audi%20Q5/Audi%20Q5%20Interior%203.jpg,
                        https://cloud.aviansoft.in/car%20images/NON%20EV/Audi%20Q5/Audi%20Q5%20Interior%206.jpg
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td>4</td>
                      <td>
                        Car Images Alt
                        <small class="text-muted">(Required)</small>
                      </td>
                      <td>
                        - Enter Images Alt/Name with coma (,) seperation (Please
                        follow the same order of 'Car Images')
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td>5</td>
                      <td>
                        Car Images Mobile
                        <small class="text-muted">(Required)</small>
                      </td>
                      <td>
                        - Enter paths of all your images in this filed<br />-
                        Make sure that use coma(,) seperation between 2 paths
                        <br />
                        - Don't use space between 2 paths<br />- Enter
                        png,jpg,jpeg,webp image file only.<br /><br />
                        For example,
                        <br />https://cloud.aviansoft.in/car%20images/NON%20EV/Audi%20Q5/Audi%20Q5%20Exterior%204.jpg,
                        https://cloud.aviansoft.in/car%20images/NON%20EV/Audi%20Q5/Audi%20Q5%20Exterior%206.jpg,
                        https://cloud.aviansoft.in/car%20images/NON%20EV/Audi%20Q5/Audi%20Q5%20Interior%203.jpg,
